**Professional Profile**
Le Nguyen Huu Duc is an emerging professional with 1 year of experience, primarily in Fullstack and Frontend Development, complemented by AI research. Duc has successfully developed multiple cross-platform applications, including a solo pharmacy store app and collaborative projects for vocabulary learning and delivery services. Key expertise includes Firebase integration for real-time data, leveraging Google Cloud APIs, and applying MVC design patterns. Additionally, Duc conducted research on prompt injection attacks in large language models, demonstrating strong analytical and problem-solving capabilities.

**Core Skills & Technology**
Proficient in Dart, Python, Java, JavaScript, and SQL. Strong expertise in Flutter for cross-platform development, Node.js, Firebase, Google Cloud APIs, Git, Android Studio, and UI Design.

**Education & Certifications**
Currently pursuing a Bachelor of Software Engineering at Ton Duc Thang University (expected 2025). Holds a TOEIC certification (Listening & Reading: 910) and has completed an Agile & Scrum Framework Course.